      <section class="about-me" id="about-me">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>
          I’m a highly disciplined and hardworking individual with a strong
          sense of self-demand and personal growth. Currently in my third year
          of a Computer Engineering degree, I combine academic commitment with a
          deep passion for technology and sports.
        </p>
        <p>
          Outside the classroom, I’m an avid athlete, constantly pushing my
          limits both mentally and physically. I hold a Dual Diploma (Spanish &
          U.S. High School) and I’ll be participating in an Erasmus program in
          Finland — an experience I’m excited to embrace both academically and
          culturally.
        </p>
        <p>
          Looking forward, I plan to pursue a Master's degree in one of three
          fields that drive me the most: Artificial Intelligence, Software
          Development, or Cybersecurity. My ultimate goal is to contribute to
          cutting-edge tech solutions while continuing to grow as a developer
          and as a person.
        </p>
